<section class="w-full bg-[#f4f7f9] py-24 md:py-32 flex justify-center px-6 border-t border-slate-100/50" id="sanctuary">
  <div class="max-w-[1100px] w-full flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-14 md:gap-16 lg:gap-20">
    
    <!-- Left: Image -->
    <div class="w-full md:w-[45%] flex justify-center">
      <div class="w-full max-w-[500px] aspect-[4/3] md:aspect-[5/4] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-slate-300/60">
        <img 
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1620641788421-7a1c342ea42e?q=80&w=1000&auto=format&fit=crop" 
          alt="Minimalist shadow on a white wall" 
          class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale opacity-90 transition-transform duration-700 hover:scale-105"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: Text Content -->
    <div class="w-full md:w-[55%] flex flex-col justify-center">
      <span class="text-[#3cbce6] text-[11px] md:text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-4 md:mb-5">
        The Sanctuary
      </span>
      
      <h2 class="text-[34px] md:text-[38px] lg:text-[44px] leading-[1.2] text-[#1e293b] font-serif italic mb-6 md:mb-8" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">
        The Atelier: A Sanctuary of Light
      </h2>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 text-[#64748b] text-[15px] md:text-[16px] leading-[1.8] font-medium" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;">
        <p>
          Our physical studio is located in a repurposed library on the outskirts of the city. We call it the "Sanctuary of Light"—a space where time feels suspended. The environment is deliberately sparse; high windows invite the shifting day inside, painting the walls with moving shadows.
        </p>
        <p>
          This physical stillness is where our digital complexity begins. We believe that to build serenity for others, one must first inhabit it.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
